General.Name: Zeotech Ltd
General.Description: Zeotech Limited operates as a mineral processing technology company in Australia. It primarily explores for kaolin deposits. The company holds 100% interests in the Abercorn project that consists of 50 sub-blocks situated in Queensland; and Toondoon project covering an area of approximately 28,000 hectares located to the south of Munduberra, Queensland. It also holds proprietary mineral processing technology for production of synthetic zeolites. The company was formerly known as Metalsearch Limited and changed its name to Zeotech Limited in December 2020. Zeotech Limited was incorporated in 2009 and is based in Brisbane, Australia.
